            "game-obj": "Sources",
            "name": "Monster Core pg. 84",
            "type": "link"
          },
          "name": "Monster Core",
          "page": 84,
          "type": "source"
        }
      ],
      "text": "Dero stalkers explore the surface world by night, seeking out victims to abduct. While hiding from the burning light of day, stalkers often assist with magisters' experiments.",
      "type": "section"
    }
  ],
