              "name": "Monster Core",
              "page": 362,
              "type": "source"
            }
          ],
          "text": "This family of humanoids are the descendants of fey creatures that fell into darkness and confusion after being abandoned in the Darklands. They are immune to confusion and vulnerable to sunlight.",
          "type": "trait"
        },
        {
